{"tid":2175240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"721目擊者：警方篡改歷史","createTime":"2020-08-26T11:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T11:24:49.000Z","uid":20933,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b15458bc7c8ca3a7f6493f45ba0234bbeba63e07","tid":2175240,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:04:40.000Z","msg":"警方下午在記者會表示，社會誤會721元朗事件是所謂「無差別襲擊」。有當日在西鐵站協助傷者的社工質疑，警方趁事件過去一年，有人淡忘事件之際扭曲事實、篡改歷史，指當日白衣人在鳳攸北街，以至西鐵站襲擊市民時，有一段長時間完全沒有所謂黑衣人在場，遇襲者包括一般市民，絕對是「無差別襲擊」。　<br />\n<br />\n他又認為警方表示用了18分鐘就到達西鐵站，是扭曲事實，說當日白衣人在元朗施襲時，警方並無介入，否則7.21風波便不會發生。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2354344&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=f28f3741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354344</a>"},{"pid":"192938cf4bf1f590e2cf3653617ce7b2fe01d1a5","tid":2175240,"uid":283539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:05:46.000Z","msg":"用左一年時間都係交咁嘅功課，所以話真係要讀多d書"},{"pid":"e00cef84ebdb0acefa9a7040a957fe41f3d95c84","tid":2175240,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:06:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfc4840c0052790b277794ae73b99ba8ecae6f71","tid":2175240,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"歷史係由當權者寫，無咩好驚訝，做返我地要做嘅野就得"},{"pid":"1d4344164a217cfed3050d87bc8913d655d1bb3f","tid":2175240,"uid":289978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"192938cf4bf1f590e2cf3653617ce7b2fe01d1a5","tid":2175240,"uid":283539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:05:46.000Z","msg":"用左一年時間都係交咁嘅功課，所以話真係要讀多d書"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:10:43.000Z","msg":"美國就黎制裁，求其抄份功課頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b594a21c8716036b1ee32c5f242f282fb209e0","tid":2175240,"uid":60434,"like":0,"di